was reading about the Duke of Norfolk. Oh, Norfolk, that's a good name. Can you
give us just a very brief outline? Is that a science fiction book or a fantasy

15:46.980 --> 15:56.240
book or just a mainstream book or what? No, it again is a porno-gothic romance,
