16:09.740 --> 16:21.900
Okay. My manuscript is a real collector's item because I'm the only one that has
it. I haven't gotten any offers for it yet, and I probably wouldn't sell it, but

16:23.140 --> 16:28.920
as years go by, it becomes more valuable. It might make up for all those
collector's items I gave away.

