Part 1 and also Purple Passage of Rip Van Winkle. Yeah, I would think you would
have enjoyed that. Okay, are we rewound and are we turned over? The tape's

18:13.440 --> 18:25.860
rolling. Okay, the tape's rolling, so we'll start talking about Oz now in light
