23:28.780 --> 23:37.960
that's one of the things that makes this fun to find out things like that. I
guess if you hadn't arbitrarily, well, I guess not arbitrarily, but if you

23:37.960 --> 23:45.700
hadn't cut it off after the first volume and said everything thereafter was
